Stelax Industries gets 3 yr contract . Stelax Industries Ltd said on Thursday it entered a three - year , $ 25 million contract with ASA Alloys for Stelax ' s entire line of stainless steel products . The value of this contract , which is renewable every three years , does not include the NUOVINOX line , which could increase the value of the contract when the slated production begins later this year , Stelax said . NUOVINOX is a carbon steel which is cladded with stainless steel , Stelax said . Most of Stelax ' s export capabilities have been committed for the remainder of the calendar years , the company said . 
